text: Robert "Rob" Rusnov is an archer from Canada. He was born on 9 December 1973 in Toronto, Ontario. Rusnov competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Rob RusnovRob RUSNOV == References == Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian archers Category:Olympians for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Toronto
